{"tid":2125730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邱騰華否認香港正成為另一大陸城市 「一国兩制賦予香港非常特殊地位」","createTime":"2020-07-26T11:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T04:00:14.000Z","uid":184679,"like":16,"dislike":274,"uniUserReply":114,"replies":[{"pid":"4b94071ce5bc7d63198376de2f3c0156f9971b4d","tid":2125730,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T11:25:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/07/20200725_PO_%E9%82%B1%E9%A8%B0%E8%8F%AF.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F07%2F20200725_PO_%25E9%2582%25B1%25E9%25A8%25B0%25E8%258F%25AF.jpeg&h=d098d0b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n邱騰華說，支持香港的基本支柱保持不變。<br />\n<br />\n儘管美國決定撤銷香港的特殊關稅地位，但本地官員否認，香港正成為另一個中國大陸城市的指控。<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟局局長邱騰華接受南華早報訪問時說，香港這座城市的獨特性和特殊優勢取決於一國兩制的原則。<br />\n<br />\n「誰是最有資格回答這個問題的人（香港只是另一個大陸城市）？是美國總統，還是香港人？還是地球村的商業社區？」他說。「在制度設計上，香港有優勢。香港因為一國兩制而有所不同。」<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華說，支持香港的基本支柱保持不變，包括法治、公平的競爭環境、獨立的司法機構以及信息的自由流通。<br />\n<br />\n他說：「支持香港成為中國大陸一個獨特的國際城市的因素，實際上是一國兩制體系，這賦予了香港非常特殊的地位，和世界貿易組織的獨立成員身份。」<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/6839370</code></pre>"},{"pid":"87e2cd935cf7e7191785d17d4d9e658b1334b65c","tid":2125730,"uid":90328,"like":107,"dislike":2,"score":105,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T11:26:31.000Z","msg":"腐乳通菜"},{"pid":"a301c933bd2444f1a866f0ed9a3b5841627d2ba6","tid":2125730,"uid":61589,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T11:27:10.000Z","msg":"腐乳華<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f78a177142be69ed5d731949c8fbbc93a28d8c","tid":2125730,"uid":153811,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T11:27:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8d00f324b828abdf24