msg":"吓？咁耐冇見，佢原來仲在生架？"},{"pid":"7f6b44ed4e0b34d32fb712b5c8a784a9c33c411d","tid":2125730,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T12:28:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"464f42f7c4bff5484285523e5bd6f00b0383da36","tid":2125730,"uid":101554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7544e382f96f05ea8c6f2046d659465642dc33a1","tid":2125730,"uid":10094,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T11:27:49.000Z","msg":"你是搞港獨麼 一國就一國兩甚麼的制 是要反國家麼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T12:29:24.000Z","msg":"是在一國一制下輕微的地區性制度差異<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a43a916f52a6d38426a9db33ae4d6a8cc24a89ab","tid":2125730,"uid":124455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T12:29:29.000Z","msg":"腐乳師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b786760ff709b42499c81f2c5ab54f23830f81ca","tid":2125730,"uid":177039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T12:29:40.000Z","msg":"邱隊長係咪見近排外交部又硬起來諗住跟下機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁耐唔上水"},{"pid":"208e74cb03adafe71987603a36b9cc8c771fbf78","tid":2125730,"uid":10035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T12:29:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/07/20200725_PO_%E9%82%B1%E9%A8%B0%E8%8F%AF.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F07%2F20200725_PO_%25E9%2582%25B1%25E9%25A8%25B0%25E8%258F%25AF.jpeg&h=d098d0b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n邱騰華說，支持香港的基本支柱保持不變。<br />\n<br />\n儘管美國決定撤銷香港的特殊關稅地位，但本地官員否認，香港正成為另一個中國大陸城市的指控。<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟局局長邱騰華接受南華早報訪問時說，香港這座城市的獨特性和特殊優勢取決於一國兩制的原則。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">「誰是最有資格回答這個問題的人（香港只是另一個大陸城市）？是美國總統，還是香港人？還是地球村的商業社區？」他說。「在制度設計上，香港有優勢。香港因為一國兩制而有所不同。」<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華說，支持香港的基本支柱保持不變，包括法治、公平的競爭環境、獨