agraising.html&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLgOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=49064aef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/curriculum-development/4-key-tasks/moral-civic/newwebsite/flagraising.html</a><br />\n平列懸掛國旗和區旗時，國旗在右，區旗在左。<br />\n<br />\n於室內展示國旗及區旗，在確定旗幟後方牆壁的「左」、「右」時，<span class=\"xx-large\">以人背向該牆而立，面向前方時的「左」、「右」為準。</span><br />\n正確應該係咁放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/69/Hong_Kong_Monetary_Authority_Reception.jpg/400px-Hong_Kong_Monetary_Authority_Reception.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F6%2F69%2FHong_Kong_Monetary_Authority_Reception.jpg%2F400px-Hong_Kong_Monetary_Authority_Reception.jpg&h=13582f96&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T12:52:31.000Z","msg":"黃屍局長暗示港大過國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14725289e7a3c3f9310487c95ca476ef9313f18e","tid":2125730,"uid":229479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T12:54:02.000Z","msg":"又嚟 又係基本法賦予"},{"pid":"812db222ddf55ee84f730d2e429870b228309511","tid":2125730,"uid":3986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T12:54:46.000Z","msg":"一國兩制腐乳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b33c05e678c88601cc1d361a96a4c4e52a3b3a","tid":2125730,"uid":275243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T12:54:51.000Z","msg":"腐乳又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2224bf20eca609c3e82764e55cc9f158171e973","tid":2125730,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T12:56:18.000Z","msg":"，"},{"pid":"76a30bae621930b7a9cfde35cb0b95a3eddb5420","tid":2125730,"uid":186181,"like":0,"dislik